      <title>贝塞尔曲线实验</title>
      <link href="/2025/12/27/%E8%B4%9D%E5%A1%9E%E5%B0%94%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/"/>
      <url>/2025/12/27/%E8%B4%9D%E5%A1%9E%E5%B0%94%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>贝塞尔曲线实验</p><h3 id="一、实验内容-项目背景"><a href="#一、实验内容-项目背景" class="headerlink" title="一、实验内容 (项目背景)"></a>一、实验内容 (项目背景)</h3><p>在计算机图形学（Computer Graphics）领域中，如何平滑地描述和绘制曲线是一个核心问题。贝塞尔曲线（Bézier Curve）由于其数学描述简洁、控制直观以及良好的几何性质，被广泛应用于矢量绘图软件（如Adobe Illustrator）、字体设计（如TrueType字体）以及CAD建模中。</p><p><strong>本实验旨在实现以下目标：</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>不依赖</strong>现成的贝塞尔曲线绘制库（如<code>scipy.interpolate</code>），仅使用Python基础数值计算库（NumPy）从零实现三次贝塞尔曲线的计算逻辑。</p></li><li><p><strong>随机生成</strong>平面上的4个控制点。</p></li><li><p><strong>绘制</strong>出这4个点定义的三次贝塞尔曲线，并同时显示控制多边形（Control Polygon），以直观展示控制点对曲线形状的影响。</p></li><li><p>深入理解贝塞尔曲线的数学原理，特别是伯恩斯坦多项式（Bernstein Polynomials）与德卡斯特里奥算法（De Casteljau’s Algorithm）的联系。</p></li></ol><hr><h3 id="二、基本原理和方法"><a href="#二、基本原理和方法" class="headerlink" title="二、基本原理和方法"></a>二、基本原理和方法</h3><p>三次贝塞尔曲线由4个控制点 $P_0, P_1, P_2, P_3$ 定义。曲线起始于 $P_0$，终止于 $P_3$，且起始切线方向为 $\vec{P_0P_1}$，终止切线方向为 $\vec{P_2P_3}$。中间的两个点 $P_1$ 和 $P_2$ 起到“牵引”作用，曲线通常不经过这两个点。</p><p>本实验的实现基于以下详细数学原理：</p><h4 id="1-代数定义：伯恩斯坦基函数-Bernstein-Basis-Polynomials"><a href="#1-代数定义：伯恩斯坦基函数-Bernstein-Basis-Polynomials" class="headerlink" title="1. 代数定义：伯恩斯坦基函数 (Bernstein Basis Polynomials)"></a>1. 代数定义：伯恩斯坦基函数 (Bernstein Basis Polynomials)</h4><p>贝塞尔曲线可以看作是控制点的加权平均，权重由伯恩斯坦多项式决定。对于参数 $t$（$t \in [0, 1]$），三次贝塞尔曲线 $B(t)$ 的显式公式为：</p><p>$$B(t) &#x3D; \sum_{i&#x3D;0}^{3} P_i B_{i,3}(t)$$</p><p>其中，$B_{i,n}(t)$ 是伯恩斯坦基函数，对于 $n&#x3D;3$（三次曲线），展开后的公式为：</p><p>$$B(t) &#x3D; (1-t)^3 P_0 + 3t(1-t)^2 P_1 + 3t^2(1-t) P_2 + t^3 P_3$$</p><ul><li><p><strong>$(1-t)^3 P_0$</strong>: 当 $t&#x3D;0$ 时，系数为1，曲线位于 $P_0$。</p></li><li><p><strong>$3t(1-t)^2 P_1$</strong>: 影响曲线起始段的弯曲程度。</p></li><li><p><strong>$3t^2(1-t) P_2$</strong>: 影响曲线结束段的弯曲程度。</p></li><li><p><strong>$t^3 P_3$</strong>: 当 $t&#x3D;1$ 时，系数为1，曲线位于 $P_3$。</p></li></ul><p>这个公式不仅通过简单的多项式加法计算出了曲线上的点，还揭示了贝塞尔曲线的<strong>凸包性质（Convex Hull Property）</strong>：如果 $t \in [0,1]$，则生成的曲线完全包含在由四个控制点构成的凸多边形内部。</p><h4 id="2-几何定义：德卡斯特里奥算法-De-Casteljau’s-Algorithm"><a href="#2-几何定义：德卡斯特里奥算法-De-Casteljau’s-Algorithm" class="headerlink" title="2. 几何定义：德卡斯特里奥算法 (De Casteljau’s Algorithm)"></a>2. 几何定义：德卡斯特里奥算法 (De Casteljau’s Algorithm)</h4><p>除了代数公式，三次贝塞尔曲线还可以通过<strong>递归线性插值</strong>来直观理解。这是一个逐层逼近的过程：</p><p>对于给定的参数 $t$，我们在每一条控制边上找到分点：</p><ol><li><p><strong>第一层插值</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>在 $P_0P_1$ 上取点 $Q_0$，使得 $P_0Q_0 : P_0P_1 &#x3D; t$。</p></li><li><p>在 $P_1P_2$ 上取点 $Q_1$，同理。</p></li><li><p>在 $P_2P_3$ 上取点 $Q_2$，同理。</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>第二层插值</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>在 $Q_0Q_1$ 连线上取点 $R_0$，使得 $Q_0R_0 : Q_0Q_1 &#x3D; t$。</p></li><li><p>在 $Q_1Q_2$ 连线上取点 $R_1$，同理。</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>第三层插值</strong>：</p><ul><li>在 $R_0R_1$ 连线上取点 $B$，使得 $R_0B : R_0R_1 &#x3D; t$。</li></ul></li></ol><p>最终得到的点 $B$ 即为曲线上对应参数 $t$ 的位置。本实验将在代码中利用显式公式进行计算，因为其在通过矩阵运算处理大量点时效率更高。</p><hr><h3 id="三、实验结果与分析"><a href="#三、实验结果与分析" class="headerlink" title="三、实验结果与分析"></a>三、实验结果与分析</h3><h4 id="1-实验代码实现"><a href="#1-实验代码实现" class="headerlink" title="1. 实验代码实现"></a>1. 实验代码实现</h4><p>本实验使用 Python 语言编写，利用 <code>numpy</code> 进行向量化计算，使用 <code>matplotlib</code> 进行可视化绘制。</p><p><strong>源代码如下:</strong></p><p>Python</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> random</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">get_random_points</span>(<span class="params">n=<span class="number">4</span>, x_range=(<span class="params"><span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">100</span></span>), y_range=(<span class="params"><span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">100</span></span>)</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    随机生成n个控制点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :param n: 控制点数量，默认为4（三次贝塞尔）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :param x_range: x轴坐标范围</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :param y_range: y轴坐标范围</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :return: shape为(n, 2)的numpy数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    points = []</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n):</span><br><span class="line">        x = random.uniform(*x_range)</span><br><span class="line">        y = random.uniform(*y_range)</span><br><span class="line">        points.append([x, y])</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> np.array(points)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">cubic_bezier_formula</span>(<span class="params">p0, p1, p2, p3, t</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    利用伯恩斯坦多项式公式计算三次贝塞尔曲线上的点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    公式: B(t) = (1-t)^3*P0 + 3t(1-t)^2*P1 + 3t^2(1-t)*P2 + t^3*P3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :param p0, p1, p2, p3: 四个控制点的坐标 (numpy array or list)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :param t: 参数 t，可以是一个浮点数或numpy数组 (范围 0-1)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    :return: 计算出的曲线坐标点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 显式公式实现，利用numpy的广播机制同时计算x和y坐标</span></span><br><span class="line">    term0 = (<span class="number">1</span> - t)**<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">    term1 = <span class="number">3</span> * t * (<span class="number">1</span> - t)**<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    term2 = <span class="number">3</span> * t**<span class="number">2</span> * (<span class="number">1</span> - t)</span><br><span class="line">    term3 = t**<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 为了支持向量化运算，需要调整维度以便广播</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 如果t是数组，reshape一下方便与点坐标相乘</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">isinstance</span>(t, np.ndarray):</span><br><span class="line">        term0 = term0.reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        term1 = term1.reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        term2 = term2.reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        term3 = term3.reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">    point = term0 * p0 + term1 * p1 + term2 * p2 + term3 * p3</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> point</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">main</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 1. 随机生成4个控制点 P0, P1, P2, P3</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;正在随机生成4个控制点...&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    control_points = get_random_points()</span><br><span class="line">    P0, P1, P2, P3 = control_points</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;P0: <span class="subst">&#123;P0&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;P1: <span class="subst">&#123;P1&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;P2: <span class="subst">&#123;P2&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;P3: <span class="subst">&#123;P3&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 2. 生成参数 t 的序列</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 从0到1生成1000个点，保证曲线足够平滑</span></span><br><span class="line">    t_values = np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1000</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 3. 计算曲线轨迹</span></span><br><span class="line">    curve_points = cubic_bezier_formula(P0, P1, P2, P3, t_values)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 4. 可视化绘图</span></span><br><span class="line">    plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">6</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 绘制贝塞尔曲线 (红色实线)</span></span><br><span class="line">    plt.plot(curve_points[:, <span class="number">0</span>], curve_points[:, <span class="number">1</span>], </span><br><span class="line">             color=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, linewidth=<span class="number">2.5</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;Cubic Bézier Curve&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 绘制控制多边形 (灰色虚线) - 连接 P0-P1-P2-P3</span></span><br><span class="line">    plt.plot(control_points[:, <span class="number">0</span>], control_points[:, <span class="number">1</span>], </span><br><span class="line">             color=<span class="string">&#x27;gray&#x27;</span>, linestyle=<span class="string">&#x27;--&#x27;</span>, marker=<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>, </span><br><span class="line">             label=<span class="string">&#x27;Control Polygon&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 标记起点和终点</span></span><br><span class="line">    plt.text(P0[<span class="number">0</span>], P0[<span class="number">1</span>], <span class="string">&#x27; P0 (Start)&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">12</span>, verticalalignment=<span class="string">&#x27;bottom&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.text(P3[<span class="number">0</span>], P3[<span class="number">1</span>], <span class="string">&#x27; P3 (End)&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">12</span>, verticalalignment=<span class="string">&#x27;bottom&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.text(P1[<span class="number">0</span>], P1[<span class="number">1</span>], <span class="string">&#x27; P1&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.text(P2[<span class="number">0</span>], P2[<span class="number">1</span>], <span class="string">&#x27; P2&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 设置图表属性</span></span><br><span class="line">    plt.title(<span class="string">&#x27;Cubic Bézier Curve with Random Control Points&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.xlabel(<span class="string">&#x27;X Coordinate&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.ylabel(<span class="string">&#x27;Y Coordinate&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.legend()</span><br><span class="line">    plt.grid(<span class="literal">True</span>, alpha=<span class="number">0.3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.axis(<span class="string">&#x27;equal&#x27;</span>) <span class="comment"># 保持坐标轴比例一致，避免图形变形</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 显示图像</span></span><br><span class="line">    plt.tight_layout()</span><br><span class="line">    plt.show()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-结果对比与分析"><a href="#2-结果对比与分析" class="headerlink" title="2. 结果对比与分析"></a>2. 结果对比与分析</h4><p>运行上述程序</p><h4 id="第一次运行"><a href="#第一次运行" class="headerlink" title="第一次运行"></a>第一次运行</h4><ol><li>随机生成4个点</li></ol><p>![[&#x2F;img&#x2F;截屏2025-12-27 21.00.13 1.png]]</p><ol start="2"><li>生成曲线<br>![[Figure_1.png]]</li></ol><h4 id="第二次运行"><a href="#第二次运行" class="headerlink" title="第二次运行"></a>第二次运行</h4><ol><li>随机生成坐标</li></ol><p>![[截屏2025-12-27 21.10.29.png]]<br>2. 生成曲线<br>![[Figure_2.png]]<br><strong>现象观察</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>起止点吻合</strong>：生成的红色曲线精确地从 $P_0$ 出发，并在 $P_3$ 结束。这验证了贝塞尔曲线的端点插值特性。</p></li><li><p><strong>切线性质</strong>：观察图像可以发现，曲线在 $P_0$ 处的切线方向与线段 $P_0P_1$ 重合，在 $P_3$ 处的切线方向与线段 $P_2P_3$ 重合。</p></li><li><p><strong>平滑度</strong>：尽管控制点之间的连线（控制多边形）是折线，但生成的贝塞尔曲线非常平滑，没有任何尖角（C1连续甚至C2连续）。</p></li><li><p><strong>牵引效果</strong>：$P_1$ 和 $P_2$ 并没有被曲线经过，而是像磁铁一样将曲线向它们的方向“拉扯”。如果 $P_1$距离 $P_0$ 很远，曲线在出发后会长时间贴近 $P_0P_1$ 的方向。</p></li></ul><hr><h3 id="德卡斯特里奥算法"><a href="#德卡斯特里奥算法" class="headerlink" title="德卡斯特里奥算法"></a>德卡斯特里奥算法</h3><ol><li>贝塞尔曲线“动态过程”的最佳方式是可视化 <strong>德卡斯特里奥算法 (De Casteljau’s Algorithm)</strong>。这个算法展示了如何通过一层层的线性插值，最终找到曲线上的点。</li></ol><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span 